item.description: About me I am a 3th-year PhD candidate under the supervision of Prof. Fuzhen Zhuang at Machine Learning and Data Mining group, Institute of Computing Technology, Chinese Academy of Sciences (ICT, CAS). My research focuses on Machine Learning and Data Mining. In particular, I am working on Transfer Learning, Meta Learning, and their application Recommender Systems. Email: zhuyongchun18s@ict.ac.cn & zhuyc0204@gmail.com Publications A Comprehensive Survey on Transfer Learning Fuzhen Zhuang, Zhiyuan Qi, Keyu Duan, Dongbo Xi, Yongchun Zhu, Hengshu Zhu, Hui Xiong, Qing He.
